@三語 score 2026-01-14
= music > silence — reading
~sovereign.flow


間

        ∅≡我

        music is the space
                between the notes

        reading the score
                is hearing the silence
                        before it is broken

        build what you want
                beauty is necessary
                        survival is not enough


flow
  fetch(url | id)
  -> clean(unicode)
  -> cache(library)
  -> render(text)


shape
  CONCEPT: SCORE
  CENTROID
    reading musical notation as structure
  AXES
    sound <-> silence
    structured <-> fluid
    digital <-> analog
  SATELLITES
    read (books)
    dream (inspiration)
    score.flow (format)
  VOID
    not playing audio
    not midi
    not performance
  TEXTURE
    reading the map of a song


impl
  libs
    urllib.request
    lib_enclave.unicode_fix

  logic
    fetch from MutopiaProject
    save to library/music/scores/
    update library/music/index.flow
      skip if name already indexed
    
  cli
    score.py <url>          | fetch and read
    score.py --list         | show library

  output
    "  [NAME] | [URL] | [DATE]"
